  <brief_title>MGCD0103 in Elderly Patients With Previously Untreated AML/High Risk MDS or Adults With Relapsed/Refractory Disease</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase II Study of MGCD0103 (MG-0103) in Patients With Acute Myelogenous Leukemia/High Risk MDS Who Are Elderly and Have Previously Untreated Disease or Who Are Adult and Have Relapsed/Refractory Disease</official_title>
