  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In this study, MGCD0103, a new anticancer drug under investigation, is given three times per
      week to elderly patients with previously untreated acute myelogenous leukemia/high risk
      myelodysplastic syndrome or adults with relapsed/refractory disease.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
